# Echarts on Cesium

Put Echarts dom on Cesium map position, watch the camera moving and stay same coordinate.

## Intro

Create Echarts dom from option list, hide the lenged and label.

AddEventListener to `viewer.camera.changed`, change Echarts postion with cartesianToCanvasCoordinates.

## DEMO

DEMO is write by vue3. Of course you can use with pure JavaScript.